##New Year's Eve, our parents sent us away from home in Hubei Province

Micro Signal thelivings

The function introduction, reconstructs our life with the narrative beauty.

We used to have some estrangement, the original resistance, studiously avoided home, gradually turned into expectations.
In the short time together, we laugh and cry, the heart closer.

Foreword

It was a war that broke out at the beginning of the new year around every ordinary, ordinary Chinese.
This is our war. We discuss it eagerly, analyze it carefully, deplore the loss of life in the disaster, are moved by the fearless spirit of the healer, and work tirelessly for the little things we can do.
The Sea of life, we walk and cherish.
Netease's "Our war" feature tells the story of how, every day, we meet the epidemic shirtless.

Our War | serialized 05

In August 2019, I told my mother I didn't want to go home for the Spring Festival at the end of the year.
I advised my mother to stay in Hangzhou and take her to the coastal cities for the Spring Festival holiday. Mother some heart, most of the life tired, can go out in the age of handy legs look, is her wish. But the next day, she insisted on going back, and asked us to go back together.
"Mengyazi, since you got married and had your baby, you haven't been home for the New Year for years. Your family misses you very much, and your aunt and uncle also want to see Xiao Bao. "
I feel small treasure is only 2 years old, toss about still have a lot of inconvenience, want to wait a few years to say again.
The year before last, your sister's family came home for the Spring Festival. Last year it was your turn. You said the baby was too young. This year you and your sister have to go home and have a 60th birthday party for your father in the first month
It dawned on me that my mother was determined to go back to Florida -- I had almost forgotten about my father's 60th birthday, and had no intention of celebrating. I couldn't say no, so I offered to talk it over with my sister.
My sister and her family live in Beijing, when she got the call, she asked me, "go back to New Year's? Watch dad get drunk and go crazy at home? Listen to his fake apology after he sobered up? LISTEN TO MOM AND DAD fight? After 30 years, haven't heard enough? Whoever wants to go back, leave me alone. "
Family Matters are hard to break, and children are tired of family matters.
From an early age, my sister and I's biggest sources of worry were our father's drinking and anger and our parents'arguments. Even when we finally had a family of our own, the relationship between our parents remained strained and the atmosphere of the family bleak and oppressive.
In recent years, the father no longer to mother "hand in" wages, he asked for financial independence, earn all their own money, only occasionally give her three or five hundred pocket money. We had several family meetings to persuade him to give the money to his mother, but he always refused.
My mother felt that my father's behavior was a total betrayal of our entire family.
Mother of course do not lack of money, over the years, my sister and I to her pension money is enough, but she is the rub of the father of the rub of money.
"You're young, you don't understand. " But for now, my mother kept repeating, "we're family. " We didn't understand, and we didn't want to. For the idea of his mother, sister indignant, "mother also want to give him a 60th birthday party? Our old family many relatives, do a birthday party, table money, tobacco and alcohol money 10,000 can not stop. "
My sister in Beijing, I in Hangzhou, are ordinary wage-earners. Go home for the Spring Festival, travel expenses, living expenses, plus a variety of relatives go gift bags, red envelopes, for his father's birthday... calculated, is not a small amount.
A big family, once the start of their own calculation, there will inevitably be grievances.
My mother knew what we were thinking, but she didn't give up until early December 2019, once again, she tried to "torture" me. How poor my family was. You could chew off half a pig's head for killing a pig in New Year's. These days are getting better and better, but it is even more difficult for us to spend the New Year together as a family. No Birthday Party this time. Next time it'll be 10 years. Your Dad's 70."
When I heard this, I became angry. "Do I have to do it for dad? Isn't it just as lively to do it for you in a few years? "
"That's the way it is in my hometown, " my mother said, almost pleading, "Your father is a man of pomp and circumstance, and you and your sister are his only pride, and he would be delighted to have a lively birthday party. Dear daughter, you persuade sister, this year's New Year back, we have a family reunion."
"In the end is not to let mom sad. " Finally, we agreed, think most of the time, family is our armor and soft rib, but occasionally is a yoke.

In December 2019, the Spring Festival is getting stronger. I bought new clothes for my mother and my children, and a set for my father, which I packed into a suitcase. Everyone in the family talked about their ticket purchases, after discussing the various plans for the birthday party: New Year's greetings, family outings, bringing the children into contact with nature; the Mother's joy was even more obvious, and she wrote down the list of New Year's items and the list of guests early, over and over again while I was facetiming my father.
Father learned that we all go home for the new year, but also to give him a birthday banquet, happily promised: "must turn over a new leaf, good performance. "
When he's sober, he still says nice things.
On New Year's Day 2020, I caught a cold and had to cancel my trip to visit my in-laws in northeast China. Then I pulled some masks out of my house and wore them to work. Hide into the study after work, try to reduce contact with family members, small treasure in the study door crying to me to hold. I held my breath and opened the door, hugged her, and flung her open and shut it at once.
"Do you feel sorry for the child, or do you hurt her? " The mother shouted at me as Xiao Bao began to cry more.
Mother worried about catching a cold, the next day to take the baby first home. Farewell, I warned: "Mom, I heard Wuhan what new virus, this bullet train will go through Wuhan, be prepared for some good. "
"The whole train is full of people, afraid of nothing! " Mother did not care.
When my mother left with Xiao Bao, I was still worried. I dug up a public number and found that at the end of December, an article about an unknown infectious disease was posted on the public number. It specifically mentioned that elderly people should pay special attention, wear a mask to reduce the risk of infection. I began to regret that I had not prepared masks for my mother and baby.
Over the next few days, I began calling every day to inquire about my mother's and Xiao Bao's health and the abnormal conditions in my hometown, my mother also patiently reported to me: "Xiao Bao is in good health, the home is all well, the only difference is that this year no pig, the family pig died, to buy from the five peaks side of the high price. "
I wondered why the pigs in Jingzhou died and the pigs in Wufeng lived. The mother laughed. "How should I know? You'll have to ask Wufeng's pigs. "
On the night of January 9,2020, I skyped with my mother and found Xiao Bao with a runny nose. Also that night, an article appeared on the Internet, mentioned the high probability of infection virus mutation, infection of a wide variety of animals. Then on January 18th, there was the "possibility of limited human-to-human transmission" .
At the sight of this vague description, I unconsciously remembered the tenacious vitality of "Wufeng's pig" .

Xiao Bao caught a cold and his mother was even more tired. "I couldn't sleep all night. I must keep an eye out for her fever. " My mother told me about a little sister in her hometown who was blinded by a high fever when she was 6 years old.
But after a moment of sadness, she spoke cheerfully about her preparations for the Spring Festival: The bedspreads in her house had been washed, and the floor panes had been wiped. She complained about the high price of pork, but still bought some, aunts and uncles also sent a variety of food, "we do not farm, the New Year goods are too much to fit in the refrigerator, waiting for you to come back to eat it. "
Looking at the video haggard old mother, still looking forward to the reunion with enthusiasm, my nose a little sour. On January 19, I couldn't wait to take Dabao and get on the train back to Jingzhou.
On the bullet train, hardly anyone wears a mask, and neither do I. Two boys nearby had been discussing the difficulty of buying train tickets, and no one had mentioned the new virus in Wuhan. At the station, I got back on the bus to go home. There were 20 people on the bus, and the girl next to me, was the only one wearing a mask, an hour and a half away, and she didn't say a word.
At ten o'clock at night in the town, two rows of Bright Street lights illuminate the road, very quiet.
My father arrived home two hours after me, complaining that his partner was driving the wrong way and carrying things home -- three bags of rice and two boxes of wine -- to Florida -- "The boss knew I was going home for my birthday this year and sent it to her. "
"Your boss is very generous! " The mother satirized Father Stingy.
"take some grain oil to come back also very good, tomorrow we start to eat. Dad This Day is hard, early rest. " I hurriedly make amends, put out half a point may cause quarrels of Mars.
Father is a change in the past grumpiness, cheerfully advised mother, "boss, you also do not see me on the angry, I issued a few thousand year-end bonus this year, all to your life. "
"A few thousand dollars is a lot? Don't think I want your dirty money. " Mother was still sharp-tongued, she said this New Year, many people, big expenses, his father should pay living expenses, "this is called AA, right? "
"I will start to work obediently tomorrow. I will do whatever you say. I will listen to the orders of the leaders. I will not cause trouble or contradict them. " My father turned to me and said, "thank you, Mengyazi, for coming back for the Spring Festival this year. ". I'm glad you and your sister volunteered to throw me a birthday party."
My father had always been a violent man, which led to a very cold relationship. Now, as he gets older, I can't help but be surprised that he can say thank you with a touch of gentleness.
Mother's eyebrows also unfurled, "the hotel urged many times, want us to order the menu, tomorrow morning we will go. "
"Yes, Sir! " The father made a salute.
Such a warm moment seemed especially rare and precious in our family. On the other hand, my husband also had good news: The in-laws had flown from the northeast to Hangzhou to pay their respects to the children and to wish the in-laws a happy birthday in Jingzhou. Just until the 23rd, sir. Come to Jingzhou together.
This is GonNa be a big family reunion. The parents could hardly contain their joy at the news. In the early hours of the morning of the 20th, a new shopping list began:
"What do the in-laws like to eat? I don't know if they are used to the spicy pot here. "
"Well, it's cold and wet here in winter. Let's get an air conditioner for their room... "

My hometown is in a town under the jurisdiction of Jingzhou. Every year at the beginning of the first month, it is a busy season for hotels of all sizes. If you want to have a banquet on the eighth day of the sixth lunar month, you have to make a reservation at least six months in advance.
I asked around the town's more spacious hotel, only a third of the customers temporarily canceled the party, and I made a verbal reservation.
But the reunion was suddenly interrupted by a phone call on the morning of the 20th.
That morning, I invited my aunt to my father's birthday party, she has always been cheerful and lively, even some prevarication. Over the phone, she asked me abruptly, "how many masks did your family buy? "
When I said no, she asked, "can you still get masks at the drugstore down the street? "
Hearing this, the father immediately expressed his dissatisfaction to his own sister, "where to do? In the banquet to give you a plate of steamed mask? "
Her younger daughter, Yao Yao, a nurse, was on duty every Spring Festival, and this year it was her turn to spend the New Year at home, she said. Last night she just got home, the suitcase did not have time to open, the hospital was called back to Wuhan in the morning, "seems to be something big. " Said, little aunt actually choked up. The father's tone was much softer. "What's there to cry about? The medical staff is the same as the soldiers. Fighting the war. It's not convenient for you to go out with your children. We'll come and pay New Year's greetings to you during the first month. "
In our local, New Year to whom, is more respect for each other's performance. But my father's kindness was rejected by my aunt on the spot. "I won't go out, and you shouldn't come to visit. Yao Yao wants me to shut the door and stay indoors. "
"What do you say? Do not want me to give you new year, I like to give you new year? ! " Father Angry. Something tells me it's not looking good. Once again, I began to turn to the news for clues, and soon I began to feel uneasy. First, she called her sister, who said she saw the news and flew to Yichang in the afternoon. She could not transfer to Wuhan. Then she called her husband to discuss whether to cancel her in-laws'trip.
When my sister and her family came back, it was dinnertime. The table was full of delicious dishes, the children were happy, the parents were smiling, the whole family was in a happy, only I was preoccupied.

Until January 21, the news made clear that the virus "can be passed from person to person" , the whole family decided not to go out first, to discuss the birthday party.
That night, he sent a video saying that a suspected case had appeared in a park in Hangzhou. I urged him to buy a mask. He said he was waiting in line at the entrance of a pharmacy. He had been waiting for nearly an hour. The in-laws also decided not to come this time, I slightly relieved, asked him, "or, you also stay in Hangzhou, do not come over. "
"What are you talking about? ! father-in-law's 60th birthday, can I not come? You can rest assured, I wear a mask all the way, do not talk to anyone, will arrive safely. " Mr. Firmly said.
I caught a glimpse of my father beside me, a smile flashing across his face.
The next morning, I decided to go out first. The New Year is coming, the streets of the town is very lively, full of people who buy New Year goods, I wear a mask shuttle in the crowd, it seems somewhat abrupt. Three pharmacies in a row, no face masks.
Into a clinic, a little bit tired, sitting in a chair for a rest. Outside came two or three patients, some said his skull pain, some said he was weak all over. Doctors wear masks and calmly diagnose and prescribe medications.
I was still not well enough, so I asked the doctor to check it out. The doctor looked at my throat, calmly said: "inflammation, the common cold, give you a few boxes of medicine. " I do not trust, "what is the new type of pneumonia? "
The doctor smiles, "which so easily gets that pneumonia, so long as is not returns from the Wuhan. "
"I took a train through Wuhan the other day... " I added.
The doctor stopped smiling for a moment and took my temperature seriously. His temperature is normal, and he told me to take every day, there are signs of fever to go to a large hospital immediately.
I went home with two boxes of cold medicine and a thermometer. I immediately hid in a small house and isolated myself. My mother sighed, "I have to hide in Hangzhou with a cold, and then hide when I come back. This time I can't run back to Hangzhou with my baby. "
"If we cancel my father's birthday party and leave Jingzhou early, will my father explode? " I whispered
"One more day, " said his sister calmly.

On the morning of January 23rd, my sister called her busy parents into the living room.
"Let's talk about something, " she said. "Wuhan is closed. " My mother nodded in bewilderment, but kept her eyes on the SAUCEPAN in the kitchen. My father asked, puzzled, "what's crazy? "
"The city is closed, traffic control, buses, subways, trains and planes have all stopped. Can you cancel your 60th birthday first and see what happens in the future? "
Mother looked at US in surprise.
"The news repeatedly warned to Reduce Staff Mobility, Dad, you see okay? " Sister explained.
"Safety First, I completely agree. " My father readily agreed, and then sent a message to friends and relatives, "support the fight against the virus, reduce the risk of infection, the birthday party canceled. "
Mother surprised to see his father, "do not do? Has Booked a hotel, invited so many people, how to do? "
"This is no joke. The notice of the notice, the change of plans are all changed plans, " the father said.
My sister and I quickly busy up, each began to call, check the news, the mother quickly turned to the kitchen turned off the fire, and hurried back to the living room asked: "The third birthday party do not do, Spring Festival? The Year of the regiment or the regiment? "
After saying this, my mother burst into tears, "I know you don't like to come back for the New Year. Your father and I always quarrel and annoy you. For many years, I look forward to this day, the whole family, children and grandchildren, a lot of a lively year together. You've only been back for two or three days, and you're not leaving again?"
For a moment, everyone at home was quiet again.

Over the years, my family has split up in order to live and learn. When my sister and I had our own little home, we rarely went back to our mother's. Occasionally return to Hubei, also be"on duty"in turn. Calculate a family sitting around the table, listening to the sound of firecrackers to welcome the New Year, has been seven or eight years ago.
My sister turned to look out of the window, and I began to cry. When the children saw the adults crying, they all began to cry. In a blink of an eye, a room full of tears.
"What do you say these words to do? Make the children all cry. " The father red eye socket, stopped the mother.
But my mother couldn't help feeling sad. She pointed to the crowded kitchen. "I've got enough food for the whole family until the 15th of the first month. Are you leaving? What about the food? "
"The children will go to work in years' time. What if they are trapped and can not go back? Take the children with you while it is still fresh. " The father comforted his mother, "I'm not leaving. I'm not going anywhere. I'm just going to stay inside with you for the Spring Festival and make sure to eat all the good food you've prepared. "
"You want to be really beautiful, your living expenses should double up! " The mother seems to be in a fit of Pique, also seems to act like a spoiled Brat.
"MORE THAN DOUBLE! I'll give you a big five-figure red envelope! " The father, who had always been very stingy, opened his palm.
Everyone laughed and the atmosphere at home became clearer.
When I called my husband, he realized the seriousness of the problem and began to buy tickets for us. At first, the second day there are tickets, but I said a few words, a short while was robbed. Looking at my parents, I think, no matter what should also accompany them over the Lunar New Year's Eve, eat a reunion dinner, together with the year-old to go, my heart pounding, "set the first day, after the New Year to go. "
After a while, first day of lunar month's plane tickets were gone, leaving only a few tickets left for New Year's Eve.
"Are you coming or not? " He said in a voice.
One side of the father said firmly: "Go tomorrow. As long as the family together, every day is the league year. "

When the tickets were booked, it was like time stopped. Everything in front of me, somehow, became unreal, like a dream.
We had some estrangement, the original resistance, deliberately avoid the home, gradually become a everyone look forward to the "Super Reunion. ". Together for a short time, the family cried and laughed, the heart closer.
On New Year's Eve, my parents got up early and kept busy in the kitchen. Stewed chicken, frozen fish, pork, meat cake, fried bamboo shoots, sausage, steamed pumpkin glutinous rice... ... do a full table of home flavor.
In China, the most ardent love of parents for their children begins in the kitchen. "We are now Tuan Nian. " My father led us to lay out chairs and wine glasses, placing chopsticks parallel to the empty bowl.
Mother poured wine into each cup and whispered: "All ancestors and ancestors, passing ghosts, come to have a meal and drink some wine. Simple rice, a vegetarian year. Bless the children healthy, safe and sound... "
Father lit a pile of paper money under the table, also read: "Give you a little money flowers, there play a small card, I wish you four rich. "
The words have been in my family for as long as I can remember, over 30 years, every year. On the eve of the Lunar New Year's Eve, when I hear this word spoken again, I feel a deep warmth and The Nostalgia of the Infinite in my heart.
For the first time in his life, his alcoholic father did not drink at the reunion dinner. He's GonNa take us to the airport, get us out of here. Waiting for the whole family to stand together in the airport lobby, because of the fear of parting sad, all of them seem a little bit at a loss.
Mother wore a mask, a pair of eyes looked at US gently, she has no tears, eyes are only a deep regret and blessing. My father, wearing a mask, smiled, "thank you for coming back. Although short, but we two old very happy, very satisfied, you take care. "
"Father, mother, Hug. " The younger sister pretends to be relaxed, smiles very exaggeratedly. But the moment she hugged her parents, tears welled up. The children are not sensible, all squeeze into a group, cheerfully shouted: "Grandma and GRANDPA, happy New Year! "
The parents fondled the children's heads lovingly and said to us, "let's go. "
Next, the two of them had to rush back to the countryside to "light up" their grandparents before dark. Jingzhou has the old custom of "fire at thirty, light at fifteen" . On the eve of the Lunar New Year, the fire in your house will burn brightly, and the graves of your ancestors will be brightly lit.
I suddenly remembered when I was a child, I like to follow my parents to "light up" . Dark night fell, people go to the ancestral graves kowtow. Everyone, young and old, can make a lot of New Year wishes. In a little while, the dark fields, the mountains will be emitting countless light and firecrackers. What would have been an appalling tomb... would have been beautiful on this day's night.
With family, there's nothing to fear from the dark. In a few hours, the New Year will come.

Postscript

I and my sister home, to the unit reported their detailed itinerary and physical condition, at home waiting to start;
The parents-in-law prepared a sumptuous dinner to welcome US home. I still worry in the mind, avoid to think alone to study to eat, wait until the next day, my cold symptom obviously alleviated;
Cousin Yao Yao officially entered the front line, said he will pay attention to safety, let us not worry about her;
To minimize going out, he went to a nearby supermarket and bought bags of rice and flour, jugs of oil, meat, vegetables and fruits, "The supermarket is well-organized and has a wide range of items, as usual. There are people at the entrance who measure body temperature and hand out masks, which will remind customers to wear masks. "
My parents, who had stayed at home, stared at each other with wide eyes every day. I asked if my mother was still able to stay, and if my father had sneaked out. She grinned, "every year during the Spring Festival, your father is like a fire burning in his rear, and he can't go home for New Year's greetings. This year, he won't go out. No one wants to welcome him. "
I asked my mother what it was like, and she said that moments like this, I think of them as falling in love
Since my sister and I, in order to have food, parents go out to make a living. When they ran together, they couldn't stop running for more than 30 years.
And this Spring Festival, parents can finally stop the pace of a hurry. They spent every waking hour together, sleeping late at home, brushing their phones, watching TV, and playing the 17-stringed instrument.
"It was one of the most peaceful and quiet times in my life, " my mother said. "I have enough to eat and drink for now, and then I will talk about it later. I am not afraid. The difficulties will pass. "

"Mengyazi, since you got married and had your baby, you haven't been home for the New Year for years. Your family misses you very much, and your aunt and uncle also want to see Xiao Bao. "

I feel small treasure is only 2 years old, toss about still have a lot of inconvenience, want to wait a few years to say again.

The year before last, your sister's family came home for the Spring Festival. Last year it was your turn. You said the baby was too young. This year you and your sister have to go home and have a 60th birthday party for your father in the first month

It dawned on me that my mother was determined to go back to Florida -- I had almost forgotten about my father's 60th birthday, and had no intention of celebrating. I couldn't say no, so I offered to talk it over with my sister.

My sister and her family live in Beijing, when she got the call, she asked me, "go back to New Year's? Watch dad get drunk and go crazy at home? Listen to his fake apology after he sobered up? LISTEN TO MOM AND DAD fight? After 30 years, haven't heard enough? Whoever wants to go back, leave me alone. "

Family Matters are hard to break, and children are tired of family matters.

From an early age, my sister and I's biggest sources of worry were our father's drinking and anger and our parents'arguments. Even when we finally had a family of our own, the relationship between our parents remained strained and the atmosphere of the family bleak and oppressive.

In recent years, the father no longer to mother "hand in" wages, he asked for financial independence, earn all their own money, only occasionally give her three or five hundred pocket money. We had several family meetings to persuade him to give the money to his mother, but he always refused.

My mother felt that my father's behavior was a total betrayal of our entire family.

Mother of course do not lack of money, over the years, my sister and I to her pension money is enough, but she is the rub of the father of the rub of money.

"You're young, you don't understand. " But for now, my mother kept repeating, "we're family. " We didn't understand, and we didn't want to. For the idea of his mother, sister indignant, "mother also want to give him a 60th birthday party? Our old family many relatives, do a birthday party, table money, tobacco and alcohol money 10,000 can not stop. "

My sister in Beijing, I in Hangzhou, are ordinary wage-earners. Go home for the Spring Festival, travel expenses, living expenses, plus a variety of relatives go gift bags, red envelopes, for his father's birthday... calculated, is not a small amount.

A big family, once the start of their own calculation, there will inevitably be grievances.

My mother knew what we were thinking, but she didn't give up until early December 2019, once again, she tried to "torture" me. How poor my family was. You could chew off half a pig's head for killing a pig in New Year's. These days are getting better and better, but it is even more difficult for us to spend the New Year together as a family. No Birthday Party this time. Next time it'll be 10 years. Your Dad's 70."

When I heard this, I became angry. "Do I have to do it for dad? Isn't it just as lively to do it for you in a few years? "

"That's the way it is in my hometown, " my mother said, almost pleading, "Your father is a man of pomp and circumstance, and you and your sister are his only pride, and he would be delighted to have a lively birthday party. Dear daughter, you persuade sister, this year's New Year back, we have a family reunion."

"In the end is not to let mom sad. " Finally, we agreed, think most of the time, family is our armor and soft rib, but occasionally is a yoke.

"What do you say these words to do? Make the children all cry. " The father red eye socket, stopped the mother.

But my mother couldn't help feeling sad. She pointed to the crowded kitchen. "I've got enough food for the whole family until the 15th of the first month. Are you leaving? What about the food? "

"The children will go to work in years' time. What if they are trapped and can not go back? Take the children with you while it is still fresh. " The father comforted his mother, "I'm not leaving. I'm not going anywhere. I'm just going to stay inside with you for the Spring Festival and make sure to eat all the good food you've prepared. "

"You want to be really beautiful, your living expenses should double up! " The mother seems to be in a fit of Pique, also seems to act like a spoiled Brat.

"MORE THAN DOUBLE! I'll give you a big five-figure red envelope! " The father, who had always been very stingy, opened his palm.

Everyone laughed and the atmosphere at home became clearer.

When I called my husband, he realized the seriousness of the problem and began to buy tickets for us. At first, the second day there are tickets, but I said a few words, a short while was robbed. Looking at my parents, I think, no matter what should also accompany them over the Lunar New Year's Eve, eat a reunion dinner, together with the year-old to go, my heart pounding, "set the first day, after the New Year to go. "

After a while, first day of lunar month's plane tickets were gone, leaving only a few tickets left for New Year's Eve.

"Are you coming or not? " He said in a voice.

One side of the father said firmly: "Go tomorrow. As long as the family together, every day is the league year. "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
When the tickets were booked, it was like time stopped. Everything in front of me, somehow, became unreal, like a dream.
We had some estrangement, the original resistance, deliberately avoid the home, gradually become a everyone look forward to the "Super Reunion. ". Together for a short time, the family cried and laughed, the heart closer.
On New Year's Eve, my parents got up early and kept busy in the kitchen. Stewed chicken, frozen fish, pork, meat cake, fried bamboo shoots, sausage, steamed pumpkin glutinous rice... ... do a full table of home flavor.
In China, the most ardent love of parents for their children begins in the kitchen. "We are now Tuan Nian. " My father led us to lay out chairs and wine glasses, placing chopsticks parallel to the empty bowl.
Mother poured wine into each cup and whispered: "All ancestors and ancestors, passing ghosts, come to have a meal and drink some wine. Simple rice, a vegetarian year. Bless the children healthy, safe and sound... "
Father lit a pile of paper money under the table, also read: "Give you a little money flowers, there play a small card, I wish you four rich. "
The words have been in my family for as long as I can remember, over 30 years, every year. On the eve of the Lunar New Year's Eve, when I hear this word spoken again, I feel a deep warmth and The Nostalgia of the Infinite in my heart.
For the first time in his life, his alcoholic father did not drink at the reunion dinner. He's GonNa take us to the airport, get us out of here. Waiting for the whole family to stand together in the airport lobby, because of the fear of parting sad, all of them seem a little bit at a loss.
Mother wore a mask, a pair of eyes looked at US gently, she has no tears, eyes are only a deep regret and blessing. My father, wearing a mask, smiled, "thank you for coming back. Although short, but we two old very happy, very satisfied, you take care. "
"Father, mother, Hug. " The younger sister pretends to be relaxed, smiles very exaggeratedly. But the moment she hugged her parents, tears welled up. The children are not sensible, all squeeze into a group, cheerfully shouted: "Grandma and GRANDPA, happy New Year! "
The parents fondled the children's heads lovingly and said to us, "let's go. "
Next, the two of them had to rush back to the countryside to "light up" their grandparents before dark. Jingzhou has the old custom of "fire at thirty, light at fifteen" . On the eve of the Lunar New Year, the fire in your house will burn brightly, and the graves of your ancestors will be brightly lit.
I suddenly remembered when I was a child, I like to follow my parents to "light up" . Dark night fell, people go to the ancestral graves kowtow. Everyone, young and old, can make a lot of New Year wishes. In a little while, the dark fields, the mountains will be emitting countless light and firecrackers. What would have been an appalling tomb... would have been beautiful on this day's night.
With family, there's nothing to fear from the dark. In a few hours, the New Year will come.

Postscript

I and my sister home, to the unit reported their detailed itinerary and physical condition, at home waiting to start;
The parents-in-law prepared a sumptuous dinner to welcome US home. I still worry in the mind, avoid to think alone to study to eat, wait until the next day, my cold symptom obviously alleviated;
Cousin Yao Yao officially entered the front line, said he will pay attention to safety, let us not worry about her;
To minimize going out, he went to a nearby supermarket and bought bags of rice and flour, jugs of oil, meat, vegetables and fruits, "The supermarket is well-organized and has a wide range of items, as usual. There are people at the entrance who measure body temperature and hand out masks, which will remind customers to wear masks. "
My parents, who had stayed at home, stared at each other with wide eyes every day. I asked if my mother was still able to stay, and if my father had sneaked out. She grinned, "every year during the Spring Festival, your father is like a fire burning in his rear, and he can't go home for New Year's greetings. This year, he won't go out. No one wants to welcome him. "
I asked my mother what it was like, and she said that moments like this, I think of them as falling in love
Since my sister and I, in order to have food, parents go out to make a living. When they ran together, they couldn't stop running for more than 30 years.
And this Spring Festival, parents can finally stop the pace of a hurry. They spent every waking hour together, sleeping late at home, brushing their phones, watching TV, and playing the 17-stringed instrument.
"It was one of the most peaceful and quiet times in my life, " my mother said. "I have enough to eat and drink for now, and then I will talk about it later. I am not afraid. The difficulties will pass. "
